"Right about now... I need all eyes up front. ${b} is heading your way. Fellas, grab some cash — you're gonna need it. Here she comes... ${b}."
"Hold on, hold on... y'all ain't ready for this one. ${b} is about to shut this stage down. Paper up, boys. This is not a drill. Here she comes... ${b}."
"Listen up, my guys. You came here for the best, and the best is about to deliver. ${b}, coming to the main stage. Open those wallets wide. The beautiful ${b}."
"Who's got cash? I hope it's you, because ${b} is about to earn every single dollar. Main stage, right now. Get comfortable — and get generous. ${b}."
"Gentlemen... I need you to do me a favor. Put that phone down, pick that cash up. ${b} is about to take the stage and she deserves your full attention. The lovely ${b}."
