"This next one's a problem, fellas — in the best way. ${b} about to hit the main stage. These ladies make their living off of what you're giving. Let's go... ${b}."
"Real talk, gentlemen. Some of y'all been sitting on that cash all night. Time to let it go. ${b} is coming to the stage. Open those wallets... the beautiful ${b}."
"Players... check this out. ${b} is about to grace the main stage. She didn't get all dressed up for nothing. Tip like you mean it. Here she comes... ${b}."
"Main stage alert, fellas. ${b} is in the building and she's heading your way. If you're close to the rail, you better have cash in hand. Don't be that guy. The one and only... ${b}."
"What's good, gentlemen. I got somebody special for you. ${b} is up next on the main stage. Trust me on this one — get your bread ready. Here she comes."
"Hey, hey, hey... main stage is about to get real interesting. ${b} is on her way out. She's worth every dollar, fellas. Open those wallets. ${b}."
